  _dialog:
  - _name: NPC
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - "(Approaches the Cat and the Ghost with a beaming smile) Well done, both of
      you! I heard the news \u2013 you took down all the enemies. You\u2019ve done
      a fantastic job!"
  - _name: Cat
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - (Purring loudly) Meow! It was a tough fight, but we did it.
  - _name: Ghost
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - (Nodding proudly) Yes, it was a great challenge, but together we prevailed.
  - _name: NPC
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - (Reaches into their bag) I have something special for you as a reward. Cat,
      this is for you.
  - _name: Cat
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - (Eyes widening in curiosity) Meow? What is it?
  - _name: NPC
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - (Hands over a beautifully crafted wand) This wand has a special enchantment.
      It allows you to summon a turret.
  - _name: Cat
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - (Takes the wand carefully, inspecting it) Meow! A turret?
  - _name: Ghost
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - (Floating closer, intrigued) How does it work?
  - _name: NPC
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - "(Smiling) It\u2019s simple. Cat, you use the wand to summon the turret. Once
      it\u2019s summoned, Ghost, you can possess it and control its attacks. It will
      give you both an edge in future battles."
  - _name: Cat
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - (Excitedly) Meow! This will be so useful.
  - _name: Ghost
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - (Nodding in agreement) Indeed, this will make us even stronger. Thank you,
      NPC.
  - _name: NPC
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - "(Nods) You\u2019ve earned it. Keep up the good work, and remember to use it
      wisely. This is just the beginning \u2013 there are more challenges ahead,
      but I know you two can handle anything."
  - _name: Cat
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - "(Nods firmly) Meow, we won\u2019t let you down."
  - _name: Ghost
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - "(Glowing softly) We\u2019ll continue to protect this realm with everything
      we have."
  - _name: NPC
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - "(Smiling warmly) That\u2019s the spirit. Now go, enjoy your well-deserved
      rest, and be ready for whatever comes next."
  - _name: Cat
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - "(Nuzzles against the NPC\u2019s leg) Meow, thank you."
  - _name: Ghost
    _image: {fileID: 0}
    _text:
    - "Farewell, friend. We\u2019ll be ready."
  _afterDialog: []
